        {"id": "set", "type": "function", "label": "set(partial | updater)", "summary": "Update state. Partial: `set({ x: 1 })`. Updater: `set(state => ({ x: state.x + 1 }))`. Does shallow merge.", "difficulty": 1, "tags": ["update"]},
